The paper discusses the security vulnerabilities and threats in wireless networks, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR) and network security (cs.NI). The paper also discusses the physical-layer security techniques, which falls under the category of information theory (cs.IT) and multimedia (cs.MM). The paper also discusses the integration of physical-layer security into existing authentication and cryptography mechanisms, which falls under the category of systems and control (cs.SY).
